{"tid":572230,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一句到尾,撐唔撐連仔ban五毛","createTime":"2018-02-25T11:40:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-25T11:42:55.000Z","uid":112846,"like":16,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2361a5e8361899bd08ce541d0fc617d830411afa","tid":572230,"uid":112846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T11:40:38.000Z","msg":"我屌果班劣等支那畜牲<br />\n污染曬成個討論區<br />\n佢地咁撚鐘意支那,咪俾佢地嘆下支那國既做法<br />\n<br />\n果班五毛俾人屌就話冇言論自由,屌人果陣就話支那安全高於言論自由<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我屌你班仆街五毛支那畜牲,香港民族同你班死仆街住埋一齊根本就係一種褻瀆,洗唔洗去你地老豆墳頭屌你地老母</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 連仔做得好<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 連仔太仁慈"},{"pid":"85490d4735d854456fa8c8ac9cfe740744f172df","tid":572230,"uid":89134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T11:42:55.000Z","msg":"Ban 哂呢啲<span style=\"color: red;\">左</span>膠先啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/25/194254_1d29baeccf87b59b36abf19476415c2e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F25%2F194254_1d29baeccf87b59b36abf19476415c2e.png&h=d5a0f4f6&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}